Turned 30 (!!!) in Paris ❤️ a deepest thank you to every single person who has made the past ten years feel like an absolute dream! I cannot wait to see what this exciting new chapter will hold. Thank you to everyone, near and far, who journeys with me ✨

A love letter from Engage!23 The Paris Experience Creative Director, @AlejandraPoupelEvents. 💌

Bienvenue à Paris! 👋

I am absolutely delighted to extend my warmest welcome to each and every one of you at Engage!23 The Paris Experience. 🇫🇷 As your host, it is my honor to bring together the crème de la crème of the wedding industry in the City of Love and Lights. ❤️

As we embark on this unforgettable journey, my team and I aim to immerse you in the quintessential Parisian experience. ✨Our carefully curated selection of venues, each boasting rich history and unparalleled charm, will transport you to a world of elegance and grandeur. 🌍Picture yourself sipping champagne in a hidden courtyard or strolling through a magnificent chateau—the possibilities are as enchanting as they are endless. 🥂

Paris, a muse to countless artists, is a city that celebrates beauty in all its forms. 🧑‍🎨From haute couture fashion to cutting-edge design, you will find yourself surrounded by the essence of artistic excellence. Prepare to be captivated by the harmonious blend of old-world sophistication and avant-garde creativity that permeates every street and every corner of this vibrant city. 

But let us not forget the heart and soul of Paris: its gastronomy. 🥐In the land of buttery croissants, delicate macarons, and the finest wines, we invite you to indulge in an epicurean feast for the senses. 👀👂👅👃Allow your taste buds to savor the flavors of France as we present you with a gastronomic journey that will leave you craving more…❗

In the words of the iconic Audrey Hepburn, “Paris is always a good idea.” 💡 And indeed, it is. As you gather here at #Engage23, let the magic of this city infuse your spirits and ignite your passions. ❤️‍🔥May these three days be filled with laughter, joy, and delightful surprises at every turn. 💥Together, let us create memories that will forever be etched in the tapestry of your hearts. 😍

Once again, welcome to Paris, where dreams unfold, and new adventures await! 🖋️

💋, Alejandra

Video: @peytonfrank

After experiencing a private shopping experience inside Maison Louis Vuitton Vendôme 🛍️, attendees strolled through the streets of Paris toward our night 2 celebrations at @icparislegrand. ✨

The InterContinental Paris Le Grand was inaugurated under Napoleon III 🔙in 1862. Tonight’s event took place in the Salon Opera, one of the most renowned ballrooms in Paris, with its opulent statues, rich gilding, a gorgeous chandelier, and parade of mirrors!🪞

This ballroom was designed by Charles Garnier (who also designed the Opera Garnier 🎭) and was listed as a National Heritage Site in 1970.📍 #engage23

Did you know that 12 million young girls every year are forced into child marriage around the world? To raise awareness of this travesty and commemorate International Day of the Girl, we gathered at the new Mikimoto flagship boutique to benefit @vowforgirls - a non- profit organization devoted to ending child marriage. 

A cultured pearl, in a carefully nurtured environment, represents the potential that can emerge when given the right conditions to thrive. 

Similarly, a young girl, when granted the opportunity to receive an education instead of being forced into child marriage, 
becomes a precious gem of knowledge and empowerment. 

Both the pearl and the girl hold the promise of growth and transformation. Just as a pearl is shaped by its environment, so too is the destiny of a girl profoundly impacted by the opportunities and support she receives, ultimately determining the richness and radiance she brings to her life and society.

Special thanks to the generosity of these women owned businesses who partnered with us on this project: 

📋 @inanyeventny 
🍽️ @creativeedgeparties 
🌼 @eastolivia 
🎻@elementmusicnyc 
🎥@peytonfrank 

Thanks also to Mikimoto for hosting us and donating a portion of each sale to @vowforgirls
